  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b92\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bcb\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bb0\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0baf \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "We look forward to the cooperation of the new President - Russian President - to further strengthen relations with Sri Lanka",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Russian President Vladimir Putin has said that he expects the cooperation of the new President Ranil Wickremesinghe to further strengthen the relations between Russia and Sri Lanka.",
        "He has expressed his confidence in his congratulatory letter to President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "The Russian Ambassador to Sri Lanka met President Ranil Wickremesinghe on Monday. During this meeting, he also handed over a congratulatory letter from Russian President Vladimir Putin.",
        "In a letter sent by the Russian President to President Ranil Wickremesinghe, the Russian President has expressed hope for further strengthening of relations between the two countries.",
        "\"I look forward to your activities as head of state to further develop constructive bilateral cooperation in various fields in the interests of the Russian people and in the interest of strengthening regional stability and security,\" Russian President Vladimir Putin added in his letter."
      ],
